For 'Dear Evan Hansen', I took on my very first theatrical production role, splitting my responsibilities between sound effects and serving as assistant RF/belt pack technician.

A major focus of this production was ensuring that the technical backbone of the show ran flawlessly. I helped checking the headsets that the actors wore and fixed problems that we encountered  during shows.
